metadata.name: Cybernetic Rektpoet
metadata.description:
"Cybernetic Rektpoet" is the first airdrop for "rektpoet" holders and was dropped to holders on 1/1/23. "rektpoet" was a free claim gift / tribute to all holders of Rektguy NFT from 12/25/22 - 1/1/23  
(rektpoet - https://opensea.io/assets/ethereum/0x9a647940da0f730dab76f5d594c83a4788899551/4)

"Cybernetic Rektpoet" includes a piece of original poetry (an acrostic) digitally handwritten by Kevin DeAngelis, inspired by OSF's "Rektguy" Collection & Community on the hoodie.

"Rektguy Acrostic"  
Roadmap? lol nice joke  
Every rektguy a free mint  
Kings ruling over the '22 bear market  
Trait & Rarity distribution rivaling punks  
Glitchy GIF PFP's unlike any other  
Utility = The community  
Your forever rektguy is waiting...

2023  
GIF, 2048 x 2048px
